\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces Three-stage ablation of the proposed pipeline. Stage 1 performs geometry bootstrap, Stage 2 refines geometry without densification, and Stage 3 conducts geometry-frozen appearance refinement. Better results are highlighted in darker orange.}}{8}{table.caption.13}\protected@file@percent }
